t;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">无</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font>3<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）支持移动端：</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Wingdings 2\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">R</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">是</font> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Wingdings 2&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">£</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">否</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; line-height: 120%; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">二、用户非操作系统软件配置要求（如浏览器、特定软件等）</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; line-height: 120%; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font>1<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）需要特定插件 &nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Wingdings 2\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">R</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">是</font> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Wingdings 2&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">£</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">否</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（勾选</font>“是”，请填写）插件名称 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\">UnityWebPlayer</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">插件容量</font> &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\">5MB</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt; line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">下载链接</font> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">https://unity3d.com/cn/webplayer &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font>2<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）其他计算终端非操作系统软件配置要求（需说明是否可提供相关软件下载服务）</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; vertical-align: top; line-height: 22pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">IE8.0</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'MS Mincho\';mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋;\r\ndisplay:none;mso-hide:all;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">‍‍</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">及以上（推荐使用</font>360浏览器极速模式）;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'MS Mincho\';mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋;\r\ndisplay:none;mso-hide:all;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">‍‍</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">UnityWebPlayer 5.3.6插件，提供下载</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; line-height: 120%; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">三、用户硬件配置要求（如主频、内存、显存、存储容量等）</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; line-height: 120%; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font>1<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）计算机硬件配置要求</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">操作系统：</font> Win7及以上；浏览器：IE8.0；处理器：Intel 2.2GHz ；内 存：4GB ；硬盘空间：80G；显卡：分辨率1280x1024；网络：1000Mbps以太网卡；显示器：14英寸以上；网速：2M。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font>2<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）其他计算终端硬件配置要求</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">无</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; line-height: 120%; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"黑体\">四、用户特殊外置硬件要求（如可穿戴设备等）</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; line-height: 120%; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font>1<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）计算机特殊外置硬件要求</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">本项目开发了网页版，校内校外均可访问学习，便于校内外师生共享。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">（</font>2<font face=\"仿宋_GB2312\">）其他计算终端特殊外置硬件要求</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 12pt;\"><font face=\"仿宋\">无</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `vr_page` VALUES (8, '申报材料', '申报材料', 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `vr_page` VALUES (9, '教学引导', '<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 80px; font-size: 24px; \"> 1、教学引导视频</div>\r\n				<div class=\"video\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n					<video width=\"560\" height=\"320\" controls=\"\" poster=\"http://wjgt.our360vr.com/home/video.png\">\r\n		                <source src=\"http://wjgt.our360vr.com/home/教学引导视频成片.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n		                您的浏览器不支持视频，请升级到新版浏览器\r\n		            </video>\r\n        		</div>\r\n        		<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 80px; font-size: 24px; \"> 2、操作手册</div>\r\n    \r\n				<div style=\"width: 600px; margin: 60px auto;\">\r\n		            <div style=\"font-size: 100px; font-weight: 600; font-family: \'宋体\'; color: #cbcbcb;\"> “ </div>\r\n		            <div style=\"font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 50px; color:#888; line-height: 20px; text-indent: 2em;\">本实验在团队成员的共同努力和相关理论的指导下，以企业危机为例，以“危\r\n机管理沟通”发生发展为主线，对危机管理沟通所需的企业危机事件评级技能、\r\n危机沟通准备会议的召开以及公告的撰写技能，与消费者危机面谈的技巧、危机\r\n沟通的原则与表达技巧等技能进行综合实训。本实验利用 3D 技术等进行构建，\r\n包括 5 个模式，分别是知识点学习模式、训练模式、实战模式、考核模式和拓展\r\n学习模式。 </div>\r\n		            <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; margin: 30px auto 60px;\">\r\n		                <a href=\"http://wjgt.our360vr.com/home/学生操作手册.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #666;\">了解更多 &gt;&gt; </a>\r\n		                  \r\n		            </div>\r\n		            <div style=\"font-size: 100px; font-weight: 600; font-family: \'宋体\'; color: #cbcbcb; text-align: right;\">”</div>\r\n		        </div>', 0, 1);

